snippet.title: GrooVR Air Drumming - A Chance To Bleed [Cyanide Summer]
snippet.description:
Just installed this today; bad gameplay by me, but great game!
Demo game FREE on Oculus App Lab: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/4011466365558046/
SideQuest: https://sidequestvr.com/app/1672

An awesome selection of songs for a demo, all very satisfying to 'drum' to. Waiting for the full game 😎
